premise_source_doc_sentence: The second expansion , Dynasty Warriors 8 : Empires was released for the PlayStation 3 , PlayStation 4 , and Xbox One on November 20 , 2014 in Japan , with North American and European versions released in February 2015 for PlayStation 4 , PlayStation 3 , Xbox One and Microsoft Windows  (  via Steam  )  .
